captions.text: Yeaaaah here we go, finally shredding again!
Wait. You have to go down now!
Why you? I can't hold that.
Inverts is when you are catapulted out of the water by the strength of your body
You hack into the water with your heels and then it goes upwards. Pam!
The feeling of flying through the air head over heels is just insane.
A really good invert... that's simply... there's nothing cooler than this."
It's damn awesome that I can always ride with Dominik.
And in the summer, we travelled the world so much. I'm super happy about that.
